                </div>
                <div class="panel panel2">
                    <div class="section4Box center-flex">WVI’s experience in 6 districts in East Nusa Tenggara and West
                        Kalimantan offers valuable lessons on how to provide water and sanitation for all.</div>
                </div>
                <div class="panel panel3">
                    <div class="section4Box center-flex">First, the role of the community is essential.</div>
                    <div class="section4Img">
                        <picture class="">
                            <source srcset="./asset/images/section-4/peran.png" media="(min-width: 768px)">
