                        </picture>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="panel panel4">
                    <div class="section4Box center-flex">To make this work, Village-Owned Enterprises are needed. They can
                        expand access to funding, allow for legal income, and build more sustainable financial systems.
                        Communities must also be empowered to manage these enterprises effectively.</div>
                    <div class="section4Img">
                        <picture class="">
                            <source srcset="./asset/images/section-4/bumd.png" media="(min-width: 768px)">
                            <source srcset="./asset/images/section-4/bumd-m.png" media="(max-width: 767px)">
