                        </picture>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="panel panel5">
                    <div class="section4Box center-flex">
                        Everyone needs to collaborate and strengthen each other—from
                        village communities to district, provincial, and national governments.</div>
                    <div class="section4Img">
                        <picture class="">
                            <source srcset="./asset/images/section-4/kolab.png" media="(min-width: 768px)">
                            <source srcset="./asset/images/section-4/kolab-m.png" media="(max-width: 767px)">
                            <img src="./asset/images/section-4/kolab.png" alt="" loading="lazy">
                        </picture>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="panel panel6">
                    <div class="section4Box center-flex">
                        With toolkits, roadmaps, and financial reporting platforms, sustainable water and sanitation
                        management can be achieved.</div>
                </div>
                <div class="panel panel7">
                    <div class="section4Box center-flex">Interested in making this happen in your area? WVI’s report and
                        policy brief can serve as your guide.</div>
